---
layout: base.njk
title: VLOG - Full Supply
description: >-
  You are invited to sign up for our FREE weekly video message that delivers
  encouragement, insight and actionable takeaways directly to your email. Sign
  me up!
pageCss: true
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import button, section %}

{% set channelUrl = "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC81odK7ATGoVkg5eTbyRUAg/" %}

{# Captured VLOG videos at time of mirror — title, id and verbatim description.
   Descriptions reproduced WORD-FOR-WORD incl. preserved source typos. #}
{% set videos = [
  {
    "title": "Salvation Secured",
