    "id": "9lye7rRoz60",
    "text": "There are moments in our lives when we want to make sense of a wrong or an injustice that&rsquo;s been done to us. Perhaps it has left you feeling forgotten, abandoned or unloved. What do you do? Where do you go? ..."
